record.title: MEASURE PLACED ON CALENDAR--S.J. RES. 14

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I understand that S.J. Res. 14 is at the desk and is due for a second reading.

record.chair: The clerk will report the joint resolution by title.
record.narrative: The legislative clerk read as follows:

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I object to further proceeding at this time.

record.chair: Objection is heard. The bill will be placed on the calendar.
